description.en:
Gogeta Inu has one vision in mind, and that is to put an end to any villains that dare cause harm to the human race. With the newly acquired form, Gogeta’s ultimate ability targets the Ethereum Blockchain. Help the Saiyan Warrior continue to reach his ultimate potential by purchasing Gogeta to battle his enemies in the Cryptoverse. 2% of every transaction with GOGETA is deducted and redistributed to our pool of holders.
Play-to-Earn Animeverse will bring together different anime themed events, while allowing those that participate to earn GOGETA.
